des: Northampton Community College is a comprehensive community college located in Northampton and Monroe counties in Eastern Pennsylvania. The only PA community college to offer dorms, Northampton's reputation for academic excellence, student satisfaction, and job and transfer placement is remarkable. Learn more about our community by downloading our free skill!
